opean monarchs and contemporary potentates reveal the intimate connection between power and the way it is packaged.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aCourts and courtiersxClothing. 0aKings and rulersxClothing. 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z97831105379940 cprintz978030010697840uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030017713840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300177138423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300177138/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-UCY